{
  "stem": "23090.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You just try to protect that you're not going to get beat up, or slapped, or beaten.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, sure enough, I get thrown to the, to the bad side, in the, in this warehouse, in that inspection point.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My dad is on the other side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in there were kapos, Ukraine kapos, and-- [SIGHING] --They were unbelievable, just unbelievable cruel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So with that, my dad saw that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He runs up to a kapo-- and this sounds like some science fiction-- and when we were evacuating, or when we were leaving, when the Jews were leaving, or any people were leaving a place, they, they, they were very creative in hiding, since your-- your worldly possessions in those days was not dollars.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was not script money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You didn't measure them by money in the bank, because those banks were never part of, of any security.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So people in those days just were trading on diamonds and [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my dad ran up to the kapo, and he says, here-- he had them hidden in his shoulders-- in the-- in the, in the shoulders in this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave them a fairly good sized diamond.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, this is my son over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't have to negotiate with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All he had do is take this diamond from him anyway, but he told him, he'd tell them where there's more, if he let me go on the other side.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, he told me to just stay there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He came over to me and told me just to stay.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- there's a pile of clothes-- there was all these clothes that was taken off.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
